; Regression test for issue #843: --strict and bucket (BZ#843)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/843
;
; The bug was that --strict would warn about the bucket account being unknown
; even though the bucket directive should implicitly declare it.
; This test verifies that no warning is produced when using bucket with --strict.

account Expenses:Food
commodity $

bucket Assets:Checking

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00

test bal --strict
             $-10.00  Assets:Checking
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
